verbose_text: Treatment of the spheroids with an interleukin-2 variant (IgG-IL2v) and carcinoembryonic antigen targeted T-cell bispecific antibody (CEA-TCB) activated T, NK and NK T cells, and enhanced immune cell invasion into the spheroids.
